Look and Learn is an AR (Augmented Reality) experience that helps with language learning
by encouraging the user to go out and explore objects in thier world to collect phrases.
The user can get the translation of that object by simply tapping on the object while
in AR mode.

The application can translate up to 86 different languages and can run on both
iOS and Android. 

