This application was created for a Mixed Reality module in Year 3. The application to be made was supposed to 
aid in a specific domain from a set of domains. I chose education, and to aid with language learning.

Sadly, many of the APIs, like the Translation API (Microsoft Translate) and Imagga (Image Recognition)
API have all their free credits used up, so I cannot provide a proper demo that you can use.